  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0db6\u0dba\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dda\u0dc3\u0dca\u2019 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A young man died after going to a 'bike race'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Piliyandala Police said that a motorcycle ridden by a young man and a motorcycle ridden by a single-wheeler collided head-on yesterday (14th) evening on the Bokundara ICC road.",
        "Pawan Heshan, a 19-year-old resident of Piliandala Pelawatta Gorakapitiya area, who was riding the motorcycle to the race, died in the accident.",
        "The other seriously injured youth has been admitted to the Colombo National Hospital for further treatment.",
        "The deceased youth was using a motorcycle that he requested from a friend while driving at high speed from Bokundara ICC road towards Horana Colombo road with another youth. The police said that the accident occurred when the two motorcycles collided head-on while the motorcycle was moving towards the south.",
        "The police say that after the two motorcycles collided head-on, the motorcycle of the young man who was participating in the race was pulled along the road along with him for about thirty meters and stopped.",
        "A police officer said that steps have been taken to admit the other youths who were seriously injured to the Werahera KDU Hospital.",
        "Police say that the motorcycle ridden by the deceased youth has been missing till now after the accident and the other motorcycle (one wheeler) was found after it was handed over to a motorcycle repair shop in Bokundara area.",
        "The post-mortem examination of the deceased youth is to be conducted at the Kalubowila Teaching Hospital.",
        "Puriyandala Police Station Officer Chief Inspector Vishwanath on the instructions of Traffic Division Station Officer Sub Inspector Lakmina Police Sergeant 31505 Sarathchandra Constables 84752 Dharmawardena 82498 Shashika Constable Ishara conducts investigations."
      ],
